ownedComment.body: AbstractBridge is a so-called "mixin" class, i. e. during the mapping to GML its properties and associations are just copied to its subclasses (Bridge and BridgePart). This mechanism allows the handling of multiple inheritance, which is not supported by some platforms like XML. Hence, Bridge is mapped to GML in a way that AbstractToplevelCityObject is its real superclass and AbstractCityObject is the real superclass of BridgePart.
